move the calluses. Do you enjoy indoor or outdoor pursuits more? I think you have lots of opportunities for leisure pursuits. I used to live in Tokyo. I still remember my maid taking me tovrrici or treat as a child but after we moved to where I now live we didn't go trick or treating anymore because it isn't popular in here."},{"pid":"ab020e84c5a9b287766c82985d019caaeb392c5b","tid":1901824,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T07:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0735e83f8713a938a4849d70d0eff17c4ff025d2","tid":1901824,"uid":394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab020e84c5a9b287766c82985d019caaeb392c5b","tid":1901824,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T07:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T15:06:16.000Z","msg":"ching sick ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25aa5643f492e26112cb931452d5bfe40456e8e5","tid":1901824,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T07:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8753dbfbc67c0d36c0336b8383fce14b25788474","tid":1901824,"uid":317485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T07:52:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}